            h3 · &nbsp;&nbsp;Research and Proposals&nbsp;&nbsp; ·

          p To start this off, ideas were put down on sticky notes and used it to form affinity diagrams. I have suggested building an app for couples only. After brainstorming and combining other ideas, we decided to design a social networking app for loyal couples only. The main goal of the app is to help long-distance couples to manage, maintain and improve their relationship for situations like loneliness, arguments and bonding. And at the same time, making a timeline that records their life events.

