          h3 · &nbsp;&nbsp;Designing Emoji&nbsp;&nbsp; ·

        p One of the big features in the app is about using emojis to alert the partner about current mood and then setting up some options of action for the partner to do. This helps to give the partner some suggestions for actions for a specific mood.

        p As emoji is a big feature, I designed a set of emojis specifically for the app. The set of emojis is designed somewhat cute, this is meant to cheer up the end user’s mood when they see the adorable emojis.

